hanhbuild - Hanh Linux packages builder
Usage: hanhbuild [Action] [Options]
Action:
-h                           Print this message
-v                           Print version
-g                           Generate database file
-F                           Fetch package(s) build file(s)
-b                           Build packages
Options:
-s=<path>                    Root directory <overwrite $SYSROOT>
-bf=<path>                   Build file
Options <for build action only>:
-d                           Do not check dependencies
-c                           Clean build
-f                           Force
-fl=<val>                    Build flag
-t=[unpack,compile,mkpkg]    Build tasks
For any questions, please consider asking on GitHub: https://github.com/hanh-linux/pachanh

